first_nft.name: Earl Campbell's Playbook: LA Rams vs Houston Oilers - September 4th, 1978 #85
first_nft.description:
Earl Campbell takes a toss, running through several Rams defenders as they rip him out of his jersey, unable to take him down. The play would earn him the moniker, "The Human Wrecking Ball." That year, Campbell would lead the league with 1,450 yards and earn the NFL Offensive Player of the Year honor.

Fans that collect all 4 Playbooks from Earl Campbell by August 9, 2021 at 11:59 PM EST will be invited to join a digital meet-and-greet with Earl himself. The collector who purchases the most Earl Campbell Playbooks within that same window will receive a signed jersey and helmet from Earl. Full terms and conditions can be found at ftx.us/hof_terms.pdf.
